{"_name": "", "type": "pdf-document", "description": {"logs": []}, "file-info": {"filename": "its-s16-003-tls-ssl-certificate-standard.pdf", "document-hash": "43c20b950f127df5e7b3dfe097cd034d9be64dd240991d1bea1cc98767faf369", "#-pages": 3, "page-hashes": [{"hash": "ff032d4f9e7c01ce7970bbb07249e40895da58afd0e682169e7d5c49815bae2e", "model": "default", "page": 1}, {"hash": "6a27e772533e94c6345bcfc94d8f6a487c46ee333b4df6f598f2bf2e03bba9f3", "model": "default", "page": 2}, {"hash": "0e1d49baf91c3d2879532e58f8bc9a5aaacb81c7b540e7d33c18051be82afa66", "model": "default", "page": 3}]}, "main-text": [{"name": "Picture", "type": "figure", "$ref": "#/figures/0"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [250.47914123535156, 664.8720092773438, 366.2220153808594, 697.7999877929688], "page": 1, "span": [0, 64]}], "text": "State Capitol P.O. Box 2062 Albany, NY 12220-0062 www.its.ny.gov", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"name": "Table", "type": "table", "$ref": "#/tables/0"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [44.234642028808594, 441.47906494140625, 240.3574981689453, 464.3337707519531], "page": 1, "span": [0, 24]}], "text": "1.0 Purpose and Benefits", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.38709259033203, 399.9000244140625, 534.5784912109375, 430.08001708984375], "page": 1, "span": [0, 169]}], "text": "The purpose of this technical standard is to normalize the deployment of Transport Layer Security (TLS) Certificates used to encrypt and authenticate state applications.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [43.99140548706055, 368.279052734375, 146.87974548339844, 391.1337585449219], "page": 1, "span": [0, 13]}], "text": "2.0 Authority", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.22721099853516, 271.5, 553.679931640625, 356.760009765625], "page": 1, "span": [0, 490]}], "text": "Section 1 of Executive Order No. 117 charges the State Chief Information Officer with overseeing and supervising the management and operations of the Office of Information Technology Services (ITS) . Section 102(2) of the State Technology Law gives the Director of ITS responsibility for the administration of ITS. Details regarding this authority can be found in NYS ITS Policy, NYS-P08-002 Authority to Establish Enterprise Information Technology (IT) Policies, Standards, and Guidelines.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [44.1063117980957, 239.87904357910156, 123.83352661132812, 262.7337646484375], "page": 1, "span": [0, 9]}], "text": "3.0 Scope", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.45355224609375, 184.3800048828125, 545.760009765625, 228.36000061035156], "page": 1, "span": [0, 205]}], "text": "This policy document applies to ITS and its employees (including full-time, part-time, and temporary employees), contractors, consultants, volunteers, interns, and ITS supported agencies (\"Client Agency\").", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [43.83371353149414, 152.759033203125, 245.64024353027344, 175.61375427246094], "page": 1, "span": [0, 25]}], "text": "4.0 Information Statement", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.2496566772461, 124.36799621582031, 261.26800537109375, 141.552001953125], "page": 1, "span": [0, 31]}], "text": "4.1 TLS Certificate Acquisition", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [70.80614471435547, 105.18000030517578, 503.49603271484375, 121.55999755859375], "page": 1, "span": [0, 81]}], "text": "All TLS Certificates must be acquired by the designated business unit within ITS.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.2216567993164, 704.2079467773438, 236.01600646972656, 721.3919677734375], "page": 2, "span": [0, 22]}], "text": "4.2 TLS Key Management", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.37603759765625, 657.4199829101562, 536.5200805664062, 701.3999633789062], "page": 2, "span": [0, 187]}], "text": "TLS private keys will be generated in a manner consistent with NYS-S14-007 Encryption Standard. It is recommended that key material be stored in a hardened Hardware Security Module (HSM).", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.2841796875, 633.0479736328125, 255.3384246826172, 650.2319946289062], "page": 2, "span": [0, 27]}], "text": "4.3 TLS Session Termination", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.38919067382812, 597.8999633789062, 533.7625732421875, 628.0799560546875], "page": 2, "span": [0, 100]}], "text": "TLS sessions must be terminated on the application delivery controller at the data center perimeter.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [72.0, 574.1399536132812, 396.8160095214844, 590.5199584960938], "page": 2, "span": [0, 62]}], "text": "Exceptions will be permitted for any of the following reasons:", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [89.70337677001953, 549.5399780273438, 534.2160034179688, 565.9199829101562], "page": 2, "span": [0, 83]}], "text": "\u00b7 The application is considered an auxiliary perimeter for the data center network.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "List-item"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [89.42466735839844, 511.0199890136719, 534.721435546875, 543.239990234375], "page": 2, "span": [0, 99]}], "text": "\u00b7 A demonstrated technical limitation exists that requires TLS to be terminated at the application.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "List-item"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.0922622680664, 484.48797607421875, 454.1759948730469, 501.6719665527344], "page": 2, "span": [0, 60]}], "text": "4.4 URL Naming Standards for Publicly Verifiable DNS Domains", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [70.87297058105469, 435.6600036621094, 538.2000732421875, 479.6399841308594], "page": 2, "span": [0, 212]}], "text": "Application URL naming is governed by NYS-P08-003 Domain Names for State Government Agencies. This policy requires that applications use the \"ny.gov\" domain structure and comply with approved URL naming patterns.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.23182678222656, 411.2879943847656, 249.93600463867188, 428.47198486328125], "page": 2, "span": [0, 25]}], "text": "4.5 Compliant TLS Domains", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.66607666015625, 390.05999755859375, 534.5759887695312, 406.44000244140625], "page": 2, "span": [0, 88]}], "text": "Certificates shall be issued and maintained for the following compliant domain patterns:", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [89.89312744140625, 365.3399963378906, 154.656005859375, 381.7200012207031], "page": 2, "span": [0, 10]}], "text": "\u00b7 *.ny.gov", "type": "paragraph", "name": "List-item"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [89.53502655029297, 348.6600036621094, 176.01600646972656, 365.0400085449219], "page": 2, "span": [0, 14]}], "text": "\u00b7 *.svc.ny.gov", "type": "paragraph", "name": "List-item"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [89.50521850585938, 331.9800109863281, 248.73599243164062, 348.3600158691406], "page": 2, "span": [0, 28]}], "text": "\u00b7 *.agency_identifier.ny.gov", "type": "paragraph", "name": "List-item"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.14811706542969, 305.5680236816406, 296.0159912109375, 322.75201416015625], "page": 2, "span": [0, 32]}], "text": "4.6 Legacy Supported TLS Domains", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.88255310058594, 284.34002685546875, 240.0959930419922, 300.72003173828125], "page": 2, "span": [0, 32]}], "text": "Support will not be provided to:", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [89.7547607421875, 259.6200256347656, 177.33599853515625, 276.0000305175781], "page": 2, "span": [0, 15]}], "text": "\u00b7 *.state.ny.us", "type": "paragraph", "name": "List-item"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [89.79866027832031, 242.94003295898438, 138.6959991455078, 259.3200378417969], "page": 2, "span": [0, 7]}], "text": "\u00b7 *.gov", "type": "paragraph", "name": "List-item"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.1548843383789, 203.34002685546875, 534.575927734375, 233.52001953125], "page": 2, "span": [0, 168]}], "text": "To facilitate migration, legacy transitional support may be provided for non-compliant domain patterns through exception granted by the State Chief Information Officer.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.20836639404297, 178.96803283691406, 342.095947265625, 196.1520233154297], "page": 2, "span": [0, 43]}], "text": "4.7 TLS Certificates for Private Namespaces", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.14311218261719, 143.94003295898438, 535.201171875, 174.12002563476562], "page": 2, "span": [0, 135]}], "text": "Applications using private DNS Namespaces (e.g., *.nyenet, *.local) will be supported by the ITS Enterprise Certificate Authority (CA).", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.59336853027344, 35.959320068359375, 124.31987762451172, 47.4133186340332], "page": 2, "span": [0, 11]}], "text": "ITS-S16-003", "type": "page-footer", "name": "Page-footer"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [492.0719909667969, 35.959320068359375, 542.639892578125, 47.4133186340332], "page": 2, "span": [0, 11]}], "text": "Page 2 of 3", "type": "page-footer", "name": "Page-footer"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [44.151607513427734, 698.9990234375, 166.43072509765625, 721.853759765625], "page": 3, "span": [0, 14]}], "text": "5.0 Compliance", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.60960388183594, 643.6199951171875, 537.4801025390625, 687.5999755859375], "page": 3, "span": [0, 230]}], "text": "This standard shall take effect upon publication. Compliance is required with all enterprise policies and standards. ITS may amend its policies and standards at any time; compliance with amended policies and standards is required.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [44.61166000366211, 611.9990234375, 264.233642578125, 634.853759765625], "page": 3, "span": [0, 28]}], "text": "6.0 Definitions of Key Terms", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [71.73775482177734, 570.2999877929688, 536.6448974609375, 600.47998046875], "page": 3, "span": [0, 115]}], "text": "Except for terms defined in this policy, all terms shall have the meanings found in http://www.its.ny.gov/glossary.", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [44.16225051879883, 524.8790283203125, 227.7490692138672, 547.7337646484375], "page": 3, "span": [0, 23]}], "text": "7.0 Contact Information", "type": "subtitle-level-1", "name": "Section-header"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [87.66331481933594, 497.1000061035156, 518.3759765625, 513.47998046875], "page": 3, "span": [0, 81]}], "text": "Submit all inquiries and requests for future enhancements to the policy owner at:", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [232.39366149902344, 472.7279968261719, 373.8959655761719, 489.9119873046875], "page": 3, "span": [0, 23]}], "text": "Chief Technology Office", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [230.51998901367188, 400.248046875, 375.93597412109375, 417.4320373535156], "page": 3, "span": [0, 23]}], "text": "Telephone: 518-402-7000", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [135.47998046875, 414.7680358886719, 470.9759826660156, 475.3919982910156], "page": 3, "span": [0, 129]}], "text": "Reference: ITS-S16-003 New York State Office of Information Technology Services Empire State Plaza P.O. Box 2062 Albany, NY 12220", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [230.51998901367188, 400.248046875, 375.93597412109375, 417.4320373535156], "page": 3, "span": [0, 23]}], "text": "Telephone: 518-402-7000", "type": "paragraph", "name": "Text"}, {"prov": [{"bbox": [96.2949447631836, 362.5800476074219, 510.12005615234375, 392.7600402832031], "p